 BREAK AFTER 2nd CHORUS:  
 Played over intro riff, then over the following chord sequence  
 which I have called the Rhythm for Solo`s.  
 Note that while the repeating pattern is playing only use an  
 F# power chord, do not play it as a major or minor chord.  
 The repeating pattern can be varied during the Bm section  
 by alternatively hammering on to the 12th fret instead of the  
 11th. I`ve written it bar by bar to show the syncopation.  
  
