     ***F#(m)            Ab+5 (E/Ab)     A             B    C#***  
  |-----------------------------------------------------------------|  
  |-----------------------------------------------------------------|  
  |-----------------------------------------------------------------|  
  |-(4)-------------------------------2-------------4----6----------|  
  |--4----------------7---------------0-------------2----4----------|  
