     His eyes seem so glazed, see the madman in his gaze  
  *CHORUS:*  
  *I'll try and show the idea of the chorus, listen for the*  
  *strumming and chord slides. At the end go back to strumming*  
  *the ***F#*** power chord as in the intro.*  
     ***F#m          E            D C# D                        E***  
  |--2------------0-------------------------------------------------|  
  |--2------------0-------------------------------------------------|  
  |--2------------1-------------------------------------------------|  
