just give you the basic idea. Both guitars are playing  
arpeggios of chords C major and then E minor, and after a while  
A minor. The progression is: C, Em, C, Em, C, Em, C, Em, C, Am,  
Em, Em. They play that twice. These are the chord formations:  
  
